description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1: Biden implodes in Stephanopoulos interview. The senile emperor has no clothes, Democrats always had an understanding of that. The Taliban has leverage over the United States. Will anyone lose their job over Afghanistan cluster? Thousands of Americans are stranded in Afghanistan, Biden’s priority is declaring war against Republican governors who oppose mandatory masks. The President can’t stop talking about Clay’s school board meeting.
